    [PATCH] x86-64: dma_ops as const
    
    The dma_ops structure can be const since it never changes
    after boot.
    
    Signed-off-by: Stephen Hemminger <shemminger@linux-foundation.org>
    Signed-off-by: Andi Kleen <ak@suse.de>

